description:
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a change of direction?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for Band 3 Senior Nursing Assistants to join our friendly team in the Endoscopy unit at Guys and St Thomas&#39; NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role involves working across our sites assisting in all areas including procedure rooms and recovery area on a rotation basis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Senior Nursing assistants with or without Endoscopy experience will be considered as full training will be given in house.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date 19th November 2020 (midnight)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview Date 4th December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rosemary Haddou, Endoscopy Sister or Reagan Jacildo Endoscopy charge Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;on extension 54060 or by email rosemary.haddou@gstt.nhs.uk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively contact Nurse in charge (Senior Staff Nurse) on extension 54059&lt;/p&gt;
